Class AppExceptions

  • java.lang.Object
    • src.system.AppExceptions

    public abstract class AppExceptions
extends java.lang.Object

    abstract class AppExceptions

    Class composed of nested classes, those classes are custom exceptions. Each "subclass" or rather nested class has its own method. It informs current controller (the one which belongs to opened scene) about an exception via alert window.
